owl:Class.rdfs:comment: An accommodation is a listing or property that is available to rent on a short-term basis on airbnb.com
An accommodation rating is the rating given to a property by a guest indicating their level of satisfaction.
An activity is a generic excursion that is available to do in Ireland.
The activity type classifies the activity into a category.
An amenity is a service available to a guest in an accommodation.
Country refers to the location where the counties are located.
Host is the owner of the accommodation that rents the property to guests.
Location is where the accommodation or activity is based.
PropertyType is the nature of the property, e.g. apartment, house, room.
Review is the comments a guest makes about the host or accommodation that is posted on Airbnb.
RoomType is the different types of rooms available to a guest.
